Package edu.usfca.cs.echan13

Class Album

java.lang.Object
edu.usfca.cs.echan13.Entity
edu.usfca.cs.echan13.Album
public class Album extends Entity
The Album class represents music albums. It stores values for the album name, artist, and number of songs. It extends the Entity class.
